</emphasis>
, but 
<emphasis id="9EB0577BFF951977B154FBD7FE9FCF6A" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="1594">P. t. tridentatus</emphasis>
was synonymized with 
<taxonomicName id="6BC4F0EAFF951977B75AFBB5FCF1CF6A" authority="tridentatus" authorityName="tridentatus (van LITH" authorityYear="1959" box="[541,847,1099,1121]" class="Insecta" family="Crabronidae" genus="Pseneo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="1594" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="tridentatus" subSpecies="tridentatus">
